ZH: 我带上了雨伞，以防万一下雨。
EN: I brought an umbrella, just in case it rains.

ZH: 她备了一些额外的食物，以防万一客人多。
EN: She prepared some extra food, in case there are many guests.

ZH: 我们听从了导游的建议，带上了很多防晒霜，以防万一晒伤。
EN: We followed the tour guide's advice and brought a lot of sunscreen, just in case we get sunburned.

ZH: 他备了充足的备用电池，以防万一电力断裂。
EN: He prepared plenty of spare batteries, in case there is a power outage.

ZH: 我交了多份申请材料，以防万一一份丢失。
EN: I submitted multiple application documents, just in case one gets lost.

ZH: 她常常备些零钱，以防万一需要找零。
EN: She always keeps some small change, in case she needs to give change.

ZH: 我学会了基本的急救知识，以防万一发生意外。
EN: I learned basic first aid knowledge, just in case there is an accident.

ZH: 她携带了急救箱，以防万一家人生病或受伤。
EN: She carries a first aid kit, in case any family member falls ill or gets injured.

ZH: 我们带了备用钥匙，以防万一锁被弄坏。
EN: We brought spare keys, just in case the lock gets damaged.

ZH: 他存了一些紧急现金，以防万一信用卡不被接受。
EN: He keeps some emergency cash, in case the credit card is not accepted.

ZH: 我备了一些吃的，以防万一我们迟到。
EN: I brought some snacks, just in case we get delayed.

ZH: 为了以防万一，我备了一本地图。
EN: Just in case, I prepared a map.

ZH: 我多买了一瓶洗发水，以防万一。
EN: I bought an extra bottle of shampoo, just in case.

ZH: 我备足了药物，以防万一生病。
EN: I stocked up on medication, just in case I get sick.

ZH: 他备了备用轮胎，以防万一车胎爆了。
EN: He brought a spare tire, just in case the tire bursts.

ZH: 以防万一我忘了带护照，我备了身份证。
EN: Just in case I forget to bring my passport, I have my ID card.

ZH: 我带了备用笔，以防万一笔没墨了。
EN: I brought spare pens, just in case the pen runs out of ink.

ZH: 我留了备用电源线，以防万一电源线损坏。
EN: I kept a spare power cord, just in case the power cord gets damaged.

ZH: 我将备用手机带在身边，以防万一手机没电。
EN: I keep a spare phone with me, just in case my phone runs out of battery.

ZH: 我带了备用眼镜，以防万一眼镜弄丢或损坏。
EN: I brought spare glasses, just in case my glasses get lost or damaged.
